data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home nestled on a spacious back corner lot in Wilderness Cove. Enjoy the nicely updated kitchen and bathrooms, offering modern convenience & style. The versatile 4th bedroom can effortlessly transform into an office, workout room or playroom, catering to your lifestyle needs. The partially enclosed back patio adds a delightful touch of flexibility, while the expansive backyard boasts a 31 foot, round above-ground pool with a Trex deck that surrounds half of it. Don't miss the hot tub just off the patio, perfect for entertaining or relaxation. Additionally, revel in the convenience of the central vacuum, water will that is attached to a sprinkler system, water softener, alarm system & the added safety of a storm shelter. Discover the convenience of a storage room & large workshop with direct entrances from the garage, for all of your storage and DIY needs. Don't miss the chance to make this your dream haven.
